Process called "is_caller_saved" takes register_name as String returns Integer:
    Note: Check if register is caller-saved per RISC-V ELF psABI
    Note: Caller-saved: ra (x1), t0-t6 (x5-x7, x28-x31), a0-a7 (x10-x17)
    Note: Accepts both architectural and ABI mnemonics

    If string_equals(register_name, "ra") is equal to 1:
        Return 1
    End If
    If string_equals(register_name, "x1") is equal to 1:
        Return 1
    End If

    If string_equals(register_name, "t0") is equal to 1:
        Return 1
    End If
    If string_equals(register_name, "x5") is equal to 1:
        Return 1
    End If

    If string_equals(register_name, "t1") is equal to 1:
        Return 1
    End If
